# Git Workflow Rules

## Before Every Commit
Run: `pnpm format`
- Fix all linting errors
- Fix all formatting issues
- Fix all TypeScript errors

## Before Opening PR
Run: `pnpm build`
- Ensure TypeScript compilation succeeds
- Ensure Vite build completes without errors

## Branch Strategy
- NEVER push directly to main
- Create feature branch from main
- Submit PR for all changes
- Wait for review before merge

## Deployment
- NEVER deploy without team approval
- Deployments require explicit authorization
